'''2.	Write a program to find the largest and smallest word in a string.
Problem Text: If string having more than one largest or smallest word than output will be -1.
'''
x=input("Enter Sentence :")
y=x.split()
a= sorted(y,key=len)
print("The largest word is: "+a[len(a)-1])
print("The smallest word is: "+a[0])

